{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act31side", "eventName": "懷黍離", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "HS-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "紡綾羅", "storyInfo": "左樂憑藉著夕借與的力量將績困在畫卷中，想要迫使這名最大的嫌疑犯就範。同時，大荒城田地的污染，已經到了難以控制的地步。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snow_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你又要走了。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次不勸我了？", "name": "年邁的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你又有哪次聽勸了呢。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可沒有你嘮叨兩句，我反而覺得心裡空蕩蕩的。", "name": "年邁的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還能走得動，手臂腿都還結實著。春天的風還是這麼冷，我也不能躺在椅子上曬太陽。", "name": "年邁的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#16$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你該知道，北邊有多危險。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#16$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是黍……你也知道，我們沒有辦法……", "name": "年邁的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#6$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們花了幾十年時間，才開闢出這點土地。可還是遠遠不夠……", "name": "年邁的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#6$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "糧食和地總是不夠的……再北一點的地方，說不定可以找到特殊的莊稼，可以種在源石污染過的土地上的莊稼。", "name": "年邁的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到時候，整片大地都可以當作我們的農田，再也不會有人忍飢挨餓。", "name": "年邁的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你更應該留下來。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#5$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找不到這種莊稼，我們就慢慢培育。十代，百代，總有一天——", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#5$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，我哪還有那麼多時間呢？", "name": "年邁的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#3$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#8$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何況，“種在源石污染土地裡的莊稼”“整片大地變成良田”，這樣的話，被人聽到，只會被當作癡人說夢吧。", "name": "年邁的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#2$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我說不過你。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#3$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老人說的話總是更有道理的。", "name": "年邁的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女性緩緩伸出一隻手，手指輕輕地握著。"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黍啊……能不能再請你看看我的手相？看看我這個老婆婆，到底還有沒有在晚年實現理想的好運氣？", "name": "年邁的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說過，我不會看的。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "年邁的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女性笑著，伸開手掌，掌心裡躺著一朵白色的小花。她將花別在眼前女孩的髮髻上。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天我在田裡發現了一朵花，應該是今年開的第一朵，我覺得應該是個好兆頭。", "name": "年邁的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說不定趕在今年收穫的時候，我就能回來了。", "name": "年邁的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你掐算著日子，燉好排骨湯等著我就好了。", "name": "年邁的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1242_1#9$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "黍啊……", "x": 500.0, "y": 400.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 22.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "嗯？", "x": 0.0, "y": 300.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 22.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "duration": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "text": "你其實一直都能看到那個未來的，對吧？", "x": 500.0, "y": 400.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 22.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "duration": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st4", "text": "……", "x": 0.0, "y": 300.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 22.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st4", "duration": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st5", "text": "你最後……", "x": 0.0, "y": 300.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 22.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st5", "duration": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st6", "text": "別……別告訴我，我可不想知道自己什麼時候會死。", "x": 500.0, "y": 400.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 22.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st6", "duration": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st6", "text": "我只是想問問……", "x": 500.0, "y": 400.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 22.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st6", "duration": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st6", "text": "我們那個萬頃良田的夢，最後實現了嗎？", "x": 500.0, "y": 400.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 22.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st6", "duration": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g1_desertedcityfield_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#4$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天師……", "name": "疲憊的職農"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黍姑娘？", "name": "疲憊的職農"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#18$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黍姑娘，我看您在這裡愣了半天了，您肯定也不捨得這片地吧。", "name": "疲憊的職農"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "山清水秀，糧食可口……我很喜歡這裡。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黍天師，您看上去這麼年輕，調來大荒城沒多久吧。", "name": "疲憊的職農"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從出生就在這裡，現在都六十七了……六十七年，也從來沒想過有一天，還得離開這裡。", "name": "疲憊的職農"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說，從神農她老人家開墾出這片農田，到現在都一千多年了。我們怎麼捨得……", "name": "疲憊的職農"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莊稼春種秋收，一年也躲不開風霜雨雪。世事不如意才是常態，我們也只能順其自然。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以後搬到移動城市裡，大家會有別的工作可做，相信會給大家妥善安排的。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們就是不明白……本來以為這兩年天氣差點，所以收成差點，大家加把勁，總能撐過去的。", "name": "疲憊的職農"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在告訴我們是這塊地出了問題……黍姑娘，你們天師懂的多，你能不能再想想辦法，救救這塊地？", "name": "疲憊的職農"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您只要告訴我們一個方法，我們也不怕辛苦，哪怕是要把這塊地整個翻一遍——", "name": "疲憊的職農"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#8$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前兩天才下過大雨，這土地怎麼……", "name": "疲憊的職農"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dkmgcvlspd"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g1_desertedcityfield_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 3.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 3.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "田邊的職農突然瞪直了眼。"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_surfacefrozen"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "田間蓄水以肉眼可見的速度消失，彷彿是地底藏著一個無底的深淵，霎時間抽乾了田地間所有水分，也抽走了土地的生命力。"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "濕潤的水田轉瞬間變成了板結的鹽鹼地，長出了無數深不見底的裂痕。"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g4_factory_outside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "站住。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "左公子。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你準備去哪？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "送到了該送的東西，見過了想見的人，也該離開了——左公子是來給在下送行？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把所有問題交代清楚前，你還不能走。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前讓我離開的是司歲台，現在讓我留下的也是司歲台……朝令夕改，在下也很難辦啊。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大荒城中出現的邪魔穢物和你有什麼關係，你對核心城的裝置有什麼圖謀？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有……一百年前，那罪人從京城逃脫，短短數月之後，他的棋子就遍佈了炎國各地，你又從中做了什麼？！", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……左公子的這些問題，在下一句都聽不明白。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就押送你去一個能說清楚問題的地方。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "左公子孤身前來，的確是勇氣可嘉。要不是時間緊迫，在下也非常願意和左公子這樣的青年才俊多聊聊。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是……要是在下不配合呢？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男人拿出一隻玉梭，除了格外精緻些，似乎沒有什麼異樣。"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "左樂看到了上面隱隱繞著的絲線。"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休想——！", "name": "左樂"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g4_factory_outside", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_watersubcreate", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_xsplashink", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.2, "channel": "s"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_landscape", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_landscape", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "fadeout": "true", "xstrength": 25.0, "ystrength": 25.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "posfrom": "-150,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晃神只有一瞬間。"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男人手中玉梭還未揚起，秉燭人的刀鋒已經抵在了他的喉嚨上。"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不過是一個普通人，沒有和你們代理人對抗的力量……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是在這幅畫卷裡，我們沒有什麼區別。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這畫卷……是我那個妹妹……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#6$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們尋常人類什麼時候也敢利用這種力量了？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#4$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你大概是低估了巨獸學士對你們的研究程度……你們每一位的能力，司歲台都瞭如指掌。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到夕居然對我意見這麼大，寧願和秉燭人合作也要來找我的麻煩……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過秉燭人私下接觸代理人不該是重罪嗎？左公子已經是戴罪之身，還要做這種出格的事，就沒有考慮過後果？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能在這裡阻止你……將你捉拿歸案就夠了。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你將邪魔污染引入大荒城，就是為了毀掉十二樓五城？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這件事背後，是不是也有那個罪人的計劃？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我說，正是如此呢？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "？！", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#5$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那左公子想怎麼做呢？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡殺了我，好讓京城地底的歲得到的神識再多一份？大炎真的做好開戰的準備了？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果這樣才能阻止你，我們會這麼做。時至今日，歲獸絕不是你們胡作非為的擋箭牌。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可到底是筆需要盤算的買賣。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 5.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "100,-30", "duration": 0.7, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男人微笑著無視抵在喉嚨上的長刀，拍了拍衣袍，找了一處石階坐了下來。"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老實點——", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何必緊張，既然都已經用這幅畫卷困住了我，現在的我不過是個手無縛羽之力的裁縫罷了。左公子難道怕我飛出去？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "機會難得，不如來聊一聊吧。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只需回答我的問題。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "左公子對藏書閣裡那些自己沒有權限接觸的卷宗，難道就不感到好奇？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大好的機會就在眼前，左公子想問的問題應該不只這些吧？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別想耍花樣……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們就來算筆帳吧。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算一筆炎國和巨獸的帳。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g8_crestofweir", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#2$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……到這裡就沒有了？", "name": "天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#2$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些被邪魔污染的種子，如果是從那條河上漂過來的，怎麼越到城邊，污染的痕跡越少……", "name": "天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#4$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難不成……", "name": "天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#4$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她捧起一把泥土在手中細細揉捻，隨即皺起了眉頭。"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地面隱隱有震動傳來，遠處新建起的移動地塊高低起伏，像是連綿的山脈，又像是荒蠻之物隆起的背脊。"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鋼筋水泥捧起有萬年歷史的土壤，龐大的造物似是架起了跨越無數歲月的橋。可又有誰知曉這土地萬年的痕跡？"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是你做的嗎？", "name": "天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#3$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多年，都是你不聲不響地壓制著這一片邪魔……你想要的是什麼？", "name": "天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#2$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪有你這樣的“神仙”……", "name": "天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#2$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_landscape", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "左公子，見過蠶嗎？或者至少該聽過一個成語，叫“作繭自縛”？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼意思？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對這些事可是熟得很。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些蟲子生長的時候總要渡過一劫，渡得過去的，破繭而出；渡不過去的，生命就在一片昏暗裡悄無聲息地停止了。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你在說誰是蟲子？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如你如我，世間萬物。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨你怎麼想，但我們可沒打算自比蟲子。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們以自己創造的文明為榮，可司歲台的資料裡，難道沒有記述最初的最初，真龍為什麼能結束百氏之亂？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們當然知道，也十分清楚那不過是歲獸出於傲慢的愚弄，絕非恩賜。難道你還想讓炎國念你們的好？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何況時至今日，你們早就不具備那樣的力量。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "毀滅新生，任何生命都逃不過。夏蟲不可語冰，我們所見所聞所思所想，其實都被包在一隻繭裡，總要保持謙遜的。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想說什麼？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從那場大戰結束，我們這些人出現，司歲台至今也有千年的歷史了。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "左公子難道就沒有考慮過，為什麼直到現在炎國才決定除歲？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "百年前，那罪人作亂，導致一名代理人身死。如今歲獸甦醒已是不可避免，除歲當然勢在必行。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歲獸將醒，是哪位巨獸學士得出的結論？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "待到炎國不得不大動干戈時，到底對誰有利好，“除歲”這件事，有沒有某些人自己的算盤？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些問題，左公子到底是沒想過，還是假裝它們不存在？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我憑什麼要聽信你的一面之詞……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然不必信我，我們來算另一筆帳吧。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "且不論我只是一介商販走卒，我那些年長的哥哥姐姐數百年來把多少危險擋在大炎國門之外。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連我那個“遊手好閒”的妹妹，要是沒有她，炎國不知道要花多少倍的力氣才能造出如今這些移動城市。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，一直守在這裡的那位姐姐……", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巨獸與炎國的歷史共生，自始至終，我的那些兄弟姐妹不曾做過危害炎國的事，他們所求，不過只是像人一樣普通地活著罷了。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而如今，他們卻要因為一些無妄之災丟了性命……左公子倒是告訴我，這筆帳又該怎麼算？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們當中有些人，的確對炎國功不可沒，炎國也從來不曾忘記。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，是你們中有人選擇站在了與大炎敵對的一面，是你們在威脅大炎億兆百姓的安全。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，左公子方才還說，所謂“神”對炎國的照顧不過爾爾，怎麼遇到一些難題，便又怪起“神”了？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪裡有“神”呢，自始至終，都只有人。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼不看看你們自己腳下呢。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gatecloz"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#2$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些受污染的莊稼，不是已經處理掉了……", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不對……這些明明是之前正常收下來的糧食，為什麼會變成這樣……", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾日前收割下來的稻穀堆滿了糧倉。"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本應是金黃色的穀堆，現在卻變成了赤黑色的小山。"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}